creator: MIV Dev
descriptionHtml:
Stream directly from your mobile device!
Features:
- Live H.264/AAC encoding.
- RTMP streaming over TCP.
- RTMPS support - SSL for RTMP.
- Front and back cameras are supported with hot switch.
- Capturing screen of your Android device and transferring it in real-time.
- Streams to any media server like Nimble Streamer, Wowza Streaming Engine...
- Streams to Facebook Live, YouTube Live, Twitch...

creator: MIV Dev
descriptionHtml:
Astra Streaming Studio allows streaming video live content from your mobile device, can be used for video streams, as an IP camera or video recorder.
- H.264/AAC encoding.
- Streams to YouTube Live.
- RTMP and RTSP streaming.
- RTMPS/RTSPS streaming over SSL, authorization support.
- Front and back cameras hot switch.
- Capture your device's screen and streaming in real-time.
- Saving to MP4, with loop recording.
- Multiple simultaneous connections support.
